rker进程</li></ul></ul><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li>worker_rlimit_core</li></ul><ul lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li>定义每个进程的内核文件大小</li><li><span>worker_rlimit_core&nbsp; 100m;</span></li></ul></ul><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li><span>worker_rlimit_nofile</span></li></ul><ul lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li>定义一个worker可以同时处理的文件数量</li><li><span>worker_rlimit_nofile 10000；</span></li></ul></ul><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li>working_directory /usr/local/nginx</li></ul><ul lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li>默认值在配置编译时通过prefix开关选项指定</li></ul></ul><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li><span style=\"color: #F5222D;\"><strong>Events模块</strong></span></li></ul><ul lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li>accept_mutex&nbsp;</li></ul></ul><ul lake-indent=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ul lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: square; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li>on/off,默认on</li><li>启用/禁用使用一个接受互斥（现象）锁来打开套接字监听</li></ul></ul></ul><ul lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li>accept_mutex_dalay</li></ul></ul><ul lake-indent=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ul lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: square; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li><span>500ms</span></li><li>定义一个worker进程在尝试再次获取资源之前应该等待多长时间</li><li><span>·accept_mutex 有效on时才会使用使用这个命令</span></li></ul></ul></ul><ul lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li>worker_connections</li></ul></ul><ul lake-indent=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ul lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: square; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li>定义一个worker进程能够同时连接的数量</li></ul></ul></ul><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li><span style=\"color: #F5222D;\"><strong>Configure模块</strong></span></li></ul><ul lake-indent=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px;\"><li>include指令</li></ul></ul><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li><br></li></ul></div>",
    "body_lake": "<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><ul><li>daemon:on/off</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>启用或禁用守护进程模式</li><li>禁用则该程序就不能在后台启动，当他在shell下运行时，将留在前端运行     </li></ul><ul><li>error_log    /file/path  level</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>默认值：logs/error.log error</li><li>使用环境：main http server location</li><li>级别：debug info notice warn error crit（详细程度由高到低）</li></ul><ul><li>log_not_found:on/off</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li><span>使用环境：main http server location</span>   </li><li>开启或禁用记录404错误</li></ul><ul><li>master_process:on/off</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>默认值on</li><li>开启则nginx将开启多个进程：一个master主进程和worker进程</li><li>禁用则Nginx则会以独一无二的进程来运行，</li><li>仅被用于测试,客户端无法连接到master进程的服务器</li></ul><ul><li> pid logs/nginx.pid</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>用于存放Nginx守护进程的pid文件路径</li><li>默认值为编译时定义</li></ul><ul><li>ssl_engine</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>语法：ssl_engine enginename(系统的有效硬件SSL加速器)                      </li></ul><ul><li>thread_stack_size</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>语法：<span>thread_stack_size 1m;</span></li><li>默认值None</li><li>定义线程堆栈的大小</li></ul><ul><li>timer_resolution</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li><span>语法：timer_resolution 10s;</span></li><li>控制系统调用gettimeofday()时间间隔</li></ul><ul><li>user</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>定义用户及其相应的个组</li><li>Nginx的worker进程将使用这些设置来运行</li><li>user username;</li></ul><ul><li>worker_threads</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>语法：<span>worker_threads 9；</span></li><li>为每一个worker进程定义一定数量的线程</li></ul><ul><li>worker_cpu_affinity</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>与worker_process协同工作</li></ul><ul><li>worker_processes</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>语法：<span>worker_processes 4；</span></li><li>定义worker进程的数量</li><li>nginx可以将请求的处理分配到多个worker进程</li></ul><ul><li>worker_rlimit_core</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>定义每个进程的内核文件大小</li><li><span>worker_rlimit_core  100m;</span></li></ul><ul><li><span>worker_rlimit_nofile</span></li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>定义一个worker可以同时处理的文件数量</li><li><span>worker_rlimit_nofile 10000；</span></li></ul><ul><li>working_directory /usr/local/nginx</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>默认值在配置编译时通过prefix开关选项指定</li></ul><ul><li><span style=\"color: #F5222D;\"><strong>Events模块</strong></span></li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>accept_mutex </li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"2\"><li>on/off,默认on</li><li>启用/禁用使用一个接受互斥（现象）锁来打开套接字监听</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>accept_mutex_dalay</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"2\"><li><span>500ms</span></li><li>定义一个worker进程在尝试再次获取资源之前应该等待多长时间</li><li><span>·accept_mutex 有效on时才会使用使用这个命令</span></li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>worker_connections</li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"2\"><li>定义一个worker进程能够同时连接的数量</li></ul><ul><li><span style=\"color: #F5222D;\"><strong>Configure模块</strong></span></li></ul><ul data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li>include指令</li></ul><ul><li><br /></li></ul>",
